<html lang='id'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='utf-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Reset Password Central Connect</title>
    <style>
      /* Standar reset untuk email client */
      body,
      table,
      td,
      a {
        -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
        -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;
      }
      table,
      td {
        mso-table-lspace: 0pt;
        mso-table-rspace: 0pt;
      }
      img {
        -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic;
        border: 0;
        height: auto;
        line-height: 100%;
        outline: none;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      table {
        border-collapse: collapse !important;
      }
      body {
        height: 100% !important;
        margin: 0 !important;
        padding: 0 !important;
        width: 100% !important;
        background-color: #f6f9fc;
      }

      /* Media Query untuk Mobile */
      @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
        .container-table {
          width: 100% !important;
        }
        .otp-text {
          font-size: 28px !important;
          letter-spacing: 4px !important;
        }
        .content-padding {
          padding: 20px !important;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <table border='0' cellpadding='0' cellspacing='0' width='100%'>
      <tr>
        <td align='center' bgcolor='#f6f9fc' style='padding: 20px 0'>
          <table
            border='0'
            cellpadding='0'
            cellspacing='0'
            width='600'
            class='container-table'
            style='
              background-color: #ffffff;
              border-radius: 8px;
              overflow: hidden;
            '
          >
            <tr>
              <td
                align='center'
                style='padding: 40px 0 20px 0; background-color: #ffffff'
              >
                <img
                  src='https://central-batam-prod.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/ckHpvCpl4DpUISo53d2XEWp0ry6WOeZbfxqPT7zYTFrwE46Cwc4jKOANvxdM.png'
                  alt='Central Connect Logo'
                  width='180'
                  style='display: block; width: 180px; max-width: 180px'
                />
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td
                align='left'
                class='content-padding'
                style="
                  padding: 40px;
                  font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
                  color: #333333;
                "
              >
                <h2
                  style='
                    margin: 0 0 20px 0;
                    font-size: 22px;
                    color: #2d3436;
                    text-align: center;
                  '
                >
                  Permintaan Reset Password
                </h2>
                <p
                  style='margin: 0 0 15px 0; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px'
                >
                  Kami menerima permintaan untuk mengatur ulang kata sandi akun
                  Anda di
                  <strong>Central Connect</strong>. Silakan gunakan kode
                  verifikasi (OTP) berikut:
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td align='center' style='padding: 0 40px'>
                <table
                  border='0'
                  cellpadding='0'
                  cellspacing='0'
                  width='100%'
                  style='background-color: #27ae60; border-radius: 12px'
                >
                  <tr>
                    <td align='center' style='padding: 25px'>
                      <p
                        class='otp-text'
                        style="
                          margin: 0;
                          font-size: 36px;
                          font-weight: bold;
                          letter-spacing: 10px;
                          color: #ffffff;
                          font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
                        "
                      >
                        {{otp}}
                      </p>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td
                align='center'
                class='content-padding'
                style="
                  padding: 40px;
                  font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
                  color: #636e72;
                "
              >
                <p
                  style='margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6'
                >
                  Kode ini hanya berlaku selama
                  <span style='color: #27ae60; font-weight: bold'>5 menit</span>.
                  Demi keamanan, jangan berikan kode ini kepada siapa pun.
                </p>
                <p style='margin: 0; font-size: 13px; font-style: italic'>
                  Jika Anda tidak merasa melakukan permintaan ini, silakan
                  abaikan email ini.
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td
                align='center'
                style='
                  padding: 30px;
                  background-color: #2d3436;
                  color: #ffffff;
                  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
                '
              >
                <p style='margin: 0; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold'>
                  Connecting Community
                </p>
                <p style='margin: 10px 0 0 0; font-size: 12px; color: #b2bec3'>
                  Â© 2025 Central Connect. Semua hak cipta dilindungi.<br />
                  Ini adalah email otomatis, mohon tidak membalas.
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>